---
---

<section id="prix" class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 md:px-8">

    <!-- Section header -->
    <p class="text-accent font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-center">Prix</p>
    <h2 class="mt-3 font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-primary text-center tracking-tight leading-tight max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Moins cher qu'un employé de réception.<br class="hidden sm:block" /> En poste 24/7.
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
      Votre gestion administrative à une <b><i>fraction du prix</i></b> d'un employé de réception.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col items-center">

      <!-- Pricing card — stacked on mobile, side-by-side on desktop -->
      <div class="relative bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-3xl w-full">

        <!-- Urgency badge -->
        <span class="absolute -top-3.5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider bg-accent text-accent-foreground px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-md whitespace-nowrap z-10">
          20 places disponibles
        </span>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">

          <!-- Left: Price -->
          <div class="md:w-[42%] p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground/60 uppercase tracking-wider">Tarif de lancement</p>

            <div class="mt-3 flex items-baseline gap-2">
              <span class="text-lg text-primary-foreground/40 line-through decoration-primary-foreground/30">299&nbsp;$</span>
              <span class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold">149&nbsp;$</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-base text-primary-foreground/50 mt-1">/ mois</span>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <a href="#commencer" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full bg-accent text-accent-foreground hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors shadow-md">
              Commencer maintenant &rarr;
            </a>

            <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-primary-foreground/35">
              vs employé de réception à temps plein : ~3&nbsp;200&nbsp;$/mois
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Divider: horizontal on mobile, vertical on desktop -->
          <div class="border-t md:border-t-0 md:border-l border-primary-foreground/10 mx-8 md:mx-0 md:my-8"></div>

          <!-- Right: Features -->
          <div class="md:w-[58%] p-8 md:p-10 flex items-center">
            <ul class="space-y-3.5 w-full">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                Disponible 24/7 — nuits, fins de semaine, jours fériés
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                Opérationnel en moins de 24 heures
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                Gère plusieurs clients en même temps
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                Connaît vos prix, votre zone et vos disponibilités
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                Conversations SMS illimitées
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
